{"tid":2299641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息：施政報告將提放寬綜援申請　保單豁免計入資產","createTime":"2020-11-25T02:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T08:01:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"f5a8ad81b71400880d2ccf2c9d4d71f2ef9ad354","tid":2299641,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:55:29.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥今日公布新一份《施政報告》。<br />\n<br />\n土地房屋方面，消息指，將提及不會放棄明日大嶼計劃，又會提出多個重建計劃，包括大坑西新邨。<br />\n<br />\n改善民生方面，會表明繼續推動60至64歲人士二元乘車優惠，亦會在一段短時間內放寬綜援申請資格，豁免計算保險現金價值，以幫助失業人士申請。 預料施政報告亦會提及發展海洋公園一帶南港島的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n政府亦會推出「大灣區青年就業計畫」，由勞工及福利局牽頭，與企業以配對形式協作，在大灣區提供職位，讓本港青年到大灣區城市工作。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2367807&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKGa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=c49c446b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367807</a>"},{"pid":"4f7113d60728b6fd2dd837c730c8f2f870eeaf01","tid":2299641,"uid":11291,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"支那新移民fat fat啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ef5b96189ac3f6a1d21a365977a4e0df131edd","tid":2299641,"uid":30145,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豁免計算保險現金價值</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係益班支那移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef51074b1206b820beb8a8e1361b3940385afcba","tid":2299641,"uid":66898,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:58:29.000Z","msg":"保單個D 唔係錢黎?"},{"pid":"7c8011e8db2a3144f12ae0b9002492c713bb56e4","tid":2299641,"uid":7482,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"e